  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist Now!</h1><p><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/5803c208660ae4a988a61b04d6b656c3.avif?t=1766156071\" width=616 height=71 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When sentient robots get left behind by their creators, they <strong>form a civilization</strong> and imitate them <strong>through artificial emotions</strong>. Unable to control these emotions, a civil war breaks out which eventually breaks them up into three different factions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Under the guidance of <i>Enigma</i>, a scientist looking to <strong>restore the former peace</strong>, players need to infiltrate enemy territory to take out the three factions leaders in one fell swoop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/a78b5f6eae6305e5bb909eb8a3975a79.avif?t=1766156071\" width=600 height=100 /></span>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against <strong>10 unique Bosses</strong>, all of which can <strong>change their behaviour depending on what you say to them.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Confront bosses with different emotions and watch them become sad, angry or happy - all of which drastically changing the flow of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The first boss might just try to melt you down if you insult her pride, but may also take it a little easier on you after receiving a compliment</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find out how each boss reacts and use their emotions to your advantage!Strong emotions bring greater rewards!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/724416e72bb7552fc0faa08b7b8b5283.poster.avif?t=1766156071\" width=536 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/724416e72bb7552fc0faa08b7b8b5283.webm?t=1766156071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/724416e72bb7552fc0faa08b7b8b5283.mp4?t=1766156071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/1060a3d15b4a9cf6ba8d4efd2e399e02.avif?t=1766156071\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>17  futuristic weapons</strong> and <strong>over 80 weapon-altering modifications.</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extra Bullets: Let your bullets spawn additional small bullets and overwhelm your enemies with a swarm of projectiles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explosions: Blow up your foes in numerous ways, make your explosions hit twice or turn them into atomic bombs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conditions: Freeze, burn, corrode and charm enemies, maybe even all at once.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create a unique build in every mission!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/e88ffbb21e7224113724a09ff2f49013.poster.avif?t=1766156071\" width=536 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/e88ffbb21e7224113724a09ff2f49013.webm?t=1766156071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/e88ffbb21e7224113724a09ff2f49013.mp4?t=1766156071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/1a17f6f1eea3bdadce9a67261732d15f.avif?t=1766156071\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 6 Emotion-based classes</strong> with <strong>27 game-changing upgrades each</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Sorrow</i> - Summon your robotic dog to distract enemies. Upgrade it to bite enemies, slow enemy bullets or become a magnet!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Love</i> - Shoot a charming Arrow. Enemies will worship you and temporarily fight their own. Upgrade it to deal damage, let enemies suffer conditions or make them hurt themselves!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each class offers many different approaches!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/d53403ecc17d4f7ca344228c9f234370.poster.avif?t=1766156071\" width=536 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/d53403ecc17d4f7ca344228c9f234370.webm?t=1766156071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/d53403ecc17d4f7ca344228c9f234370.mp4?t=1766156071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/540469961fc33aa17fc68a3aebcbeceb.avif?t=1766156071\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Base Building</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform a barren junkyard into a functional base of operations.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Recruit helpers</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet friendly robots and invite them to help your cause.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local Co-op Multiplayer</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plug in controllers and enter bullet hell in teams of up to 4 players!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Mission into the 3 factions will be the same</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each region will shuffle up their rooms and enemies with every run. There's always something new to discover!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/a5a3840fb751a33a1685f9383b1a030c.poster.avif?t=1766156071\" width=500 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/a5a3840fb751a33a1685f9383b1a030c.webm?t=1766156071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/a5a3840fb751a33a1685f9383b1a030c.mp4?t=1766156071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
