cruit helpers</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet friendly robots and invite them to help your cause.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local Co-op Multiplayer</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plug in controllers and enter bullet hell in teams of up to 4 players!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Mission into the 3 factions will be the same</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each region will shuffle up their rooms and enemies with every run. There's always something new to discover!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/a5a3840fb751a33a1685f9383b1a030c.poster.avif?t=1766156071\" width=500 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/a5a3840fb751a33a1685f9383b1a030c.webm?t=1766156071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956770/extras/a5a3840fb751a33a1685f9383b1a030c.mp4?t=1766156071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
